comments: Turner (IND) takes an extra step forward and establishes a wide screening position prior to initiating foot-to-foot contact with Davis (SAC), dislodging Davis as the pick is set.
Davis (SAC) is already in Turner's (IND) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together in the lane.
Turner (IND) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Monk (SAC) brings his hands toward Hield's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs with Hield's front/right arm as he drives inside the perimeter.
Monk (SAC) legally contests Nesmith's (IND) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Sabonis (SAC) is firming up over his left foot as he establishes himself in Haliburton's (IND) path and he does not deliver illegal contact.
Nesmith (IND) brings his arm into a vertical position prior to incidental contact occurring with Monk's (SAC) right arm during the driving shot attempt.
Turner (IND) cleanly blocks the shot attempt prior to when the ball reaches its apex.
Sabonis (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball and the part of Turner's (IND) hand that is on the ball, dislodging it away from Turner along the baseline.
Possession is awarded to IND. However, Turner's (IND) right hand touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds. Possession should have been awarded to SAC.
IND does not bring the ball across half-court within eight seconds of the start of the possession.
Nembhard (IND) brings his left arm toward Barnes' (SAC) path and marginal contact occurs with Barnes' side/arm as he drives inside the perimeter.
Nembhard (IND) makes clean forearm contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Barnes (SAC) in the lane.
Nembhard (IND) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Turner (IND) immediately slides his hand off of Sabonis' (SAC) side and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Turner (IND) maintains a rested hand on Monk's (SAC) side and marginal contact occurs as Monk elevates to pass.
Sabonis (SAC) brushes Nesmith's (IND) right arm and marginal contact occurs after Nesmith secures the mishandled pass.
Davis (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Haliburton (IND) as simultaneous marginal contact occurs with Haliburton's right side.
Haliburton (IND) legally goes into the backcourt to retrieve the loose ball after it is dislodged by Davis (SAC).
Turner (IND) establishes himself in Davis' (SAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Davis (SAC) and Turner (IND) come together at the same spot off-ball and marginal contact occurs.
Huerter (SAC) legally contests Hield's (IND) shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) and Nesmith (IND) each make clean contact with the ball prior to incidental contact occurring during the rebound.
Sabonis (SAC) and Nesmith (IND) each make clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental arm contact occurs during the rebound.
Nembhard (IND) legally contests Barnes' (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Turner (IND) moves to box out Sabonis (SAC) and marginal body contact occurs as they come together after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Nesmith (IND) brings his hand to Sabonis' (SAC) back and marginal contact occurs as Nesmith releases away to retrieve the rebound as it falls overhead.
Huerter (SAC) attempts to commit a take foul on Nesmith (IND) and the contact to Nesmith's right arm is marginal.
Barnes (SAC) avoids making contact with Nembhard (IND) as he attempts to commit a take foul.
Davis (SAC) avoids making contact with Nembhard (IND) as he attempts to commit a take foul.
